00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,051
Mika.

193
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:46,041
Phụ thân!

194
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,851
Mika.

195
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:51,161
Phụ thân!

